Interface PsiRecursiveVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnySupers, AstBufferUtil.BufferVisitor, BraceEnforcer, ClassMemberReferencesVisitor, ClassThisReferencesVisitor, ControlFlowBuilder, CyclomaticComplexityVisitor, DynamicFeaturesVisitor, ElementNeedsThis, GeneratedMarkerVisitor, GrClassMemberReferenceVisitor, GrNamedArgumentSearchVisitor, GroovyBraceEnforcer, GroovyRecursiveElementVisitor, HtmlQuotesFormatPreprocessor.HtmlQuotesConverter, ImportsFormatter, InaccessibleElementVisitor, InnerClassReferenceVisitor, IntroduceParameterProcessor.AnySameNameVariables, IntroduceParameterProcessor.AnySupers, JavaArrangementVisitor, JavaCompilingVisitor, JavaConstantExpressionEvaluator, JavaFxImportsOptimizer.JavaFxUsedClassesVisitor, JavaJspRecursiveElementVisitor, JavaRecursiveElementVisitor, JavaRecursiveElementWalkingVisitor, JavaUnresolvableLocalCollisionDetector.ConflictingLocalVariablesVisitor, JsonRecursiveElementVisitor, MicrodataUtil.CollectNamesByMicrodataVisitor, MicrodataUtil.CollectNamesFromSchemaOrgVisitor, NamespaceCollector, PsiExpressionTrimRenderer, PsiFilter.Visitor, PsiImplUtil.GroovyBufferVisitor, PsiRecursiveElementVisitor, PsiRecursiveElementWalkingVisitor, PsiVisitors.FilteringPsiRecursiveElementWalkingVisitor, PyControlFlowBuilder, PyPreFormatProcessor.PyCommentFormatter, PyRecursiveElementVisitor, PySmartStepIntoVariantVisitor, PyTypeAssertionEvaluator, RecursiveTreeElementVisitor, RecursiveTreeElementWalkingVisitor, ReferencedElementsCollector, RegExpRecursiveElementVisitor, SerialVersionUIDBuilder, TypeParametersVisitor, UnnecessaryFullyQualifiedNameInspection.QualificationRemover, VariableAssignedVisitor, VictimCollector, Visitor, XmlCompilingVisitor, XmlRecursiveElementVisitor, XmlRecursiveElementWalkingVisitor, YamlRecursivePsiElementVisitor

    public interface PsiRecursiveVisitor
    Please use this interface to mark recursive visitors. This information can then be used by the runtime to find accidental performance issues, e.g. see assertions in com.intellij.codeInspection.LocalInspectionTool#processFile and com.intellij.codeInspection.InspectionEngine#createVisitorAndAcceptElements.
